Yeah.

00:14:57.160 --> 00:14:58.460
&gt;&gt; Bill Roorbach: So did you have
to do research to find a condition

00:14:58.460 --> 00:15:01.950
that you could reasonably assume
was the condition of your aunt

00:15:01.950 --> 00:15:04.420
