It can be a good thing.

00:17:17.040 --> 00:17:18.340
&gt;&gt; Bill Roorbach: It
can be a good thing.

00:17:18.340 --> 00:17:19.640
&gt;&gt; Brad Watson: Yeah, yeah.

00:17:19.640 --> 00:17:21.050
&gt;&gt; Bill Roorbach: And that
