00:17:31.970 --> 00:17:33.270
&gt;&gt; Brad Watson: Yeah, her meadow.

00:17:33.270 --> 00:17:34.570
&gt;&gt; Bill Roorbach: Her meadow.

00:17:34.570 --> 00:17:35.870
&gt;&gt; Brad Watson: Her meadow.

00:17:35.870 --> 00:17:37.170
Her meadow.

00:17:37.170 --> 00:17:38.470
&gt;&gt; Bill Roorbach: Yeah.

00:17:38.470 --> 00:17:40.330
&gt;&gt; Brad Watson: Well, you know,
I've been in Wyoming 12 years now.

00:17:40.330 --> 00:17:43.300
When I was writing <i>Heaven to
Mercury</i> set in the same --

00:17:43.300 --> 00:17:48.350
set in the town near where Jane
