00:19:22.770 --> 00:19:24.490
&gt;&gt; Bill Roorbach: And
it's kind of a dream

00:19:24.490 --> 00:19:27.210
that grows in your imagination.

00:19:27.210 --> 00:19:28.510
&gt;&gt; Brad Watson: Yeah.

00:19:28.510 --> 00:19:31.200
But I had to go and be there
