00:20:01.800 --> 00:20:03.100
&gt;&gt; Bill Roorbach: At that point.

00:20:03.100 --> 00:20:04.400
&gt;&gt; Brad Watson: But
it takes a while.

00:20:04.400 --> 00:20:05.700
&gt;&gt; Bill Roorbach: Once
